Reviews
Reviews Summary
This summary was created by AI, based on recent reviews.
Powered by AI
Naman Retreat is often depicted as a haven of relaxation and luxury, nestled in a pristine setting that's perfect for nature lovers. Guests have lauded the exceptional service, particularly from individuals like Min and Lily, and the strategic location that offers convenience to both Danang and Hoi An. While the rooms are spacious and some feature private pools, there are suggestions for improvement in the basic amenities offered.

The cleanliness of the hotel consistently receives positive feedback. Amenities, including the spa and dining options, are widely praised, although opinions on value diverge, with some guests finding certain prices steep.
