Mark M wrote a review Jan 2024
Jersey, United Kingdom65 contributions96 helpful votes
+1
A Hidden Gem
Driving into the property your initial thought is ‘have I made a big mistake’. An unfinished road, a pretty cramped and ordinary lobby but that’s where the mediocrity finished. On checking in we were offered a discounted upgrade to a one bedroom Villa with private pool, super value for money. My partner was very impressed by the complimentary daily massage. The pool and attached bar offer the most beautiful view over the beach, a view that persuaded me to stay for an additional 3 nights. The service throughout the property was excellent and a particular mention for Min who was our lead contact throughout the stay, thank you. Take advantage of the shuttle into Hoi An, go to Bana Hills for the cable car experience the rest is very Disney, play Danang Golf Course rather than…
Date of stay: January 2024
