shinjijp1013 wrote a review Dec 2023
Tokyo, Japan2 contributions
Best hospitality experience for private family vacation.
Hotel is not huge but perfect size to enjoy private family vacation. We stayed at the villa with private pool and it was gorgeous. Foods (Vietnamese/Western/Mexican/Asian) are really good and can enjoy at restaurants and also room service. The most unique point we feel good hospitality was the direct SNS communication with the dedicated hotel person. Local tour arrangements, restaurant booking, refill mini bar… anything we need during our stay, just text her and she supported us very friendly and timely. Our window person was “Ms. MIN” and she was fantastic and made our family trip unforgettable. Highly recommend: )
Dear Sir/Madam, On behalf of Naman Team, thank you for choosing our Naman Retreat on this vacation and thank you for your kind words. We are pleased to know everything came up positively and that you will keep good memories of your holiday. We appreciate your positive feedback to our Ambassador MIN. I am delighted to share this comment to the team to enhance our service better. We look forward to welcoming you back for another great stay and do not hesitate to contact our team at reservations@namanretreat.com to receive the details of more special promotion for loyalty guests. Kind Regards, Thao Pham Front Office Manager
