Jeve C wrote a review Dec 2023
6 contributions
Stay here. Miss it. Miss out.
This place is special. Min is awesome. All the staff were great and seem to actually like their jobs and working with each other. Stay here. You won’t regret it. I booked one night and then extended for an extra x2 nights. Service is exceptional. Pool Food was a tad mediocre. The Mexican place was awesome. breakfast was great. This place is a vibe. Book. I got a good deal on my extra 2 nights by booking direct (via the website).
Dear valued Guest, Thank you for sharing your wonderful stay experience with us. We are delighted that you made the most out of your stay. Our pool villa is indeed a great choice to indulge yourself in a relaxing vacation. We thank you as well for your kind words towards our associate, especially Min. We look forward to see you again next time you are back in Da Nang. Should you have any further inquiry, please do not hesitate to contact us. Kind Regards, Thao Pham Front Office Manager
Sachin S wrote a review Dec 2023
Great experience at Naman
It was a wonderful trip, the staff is excellent the rooms are very comfortable and spacious, plenty of pools, the Mexican and Vietnamese food I tried was also very good. But what made it the best is "Helen" she was my ambassador and I texted her 5-10 times a day to ask her for favors from laundry, room service, car service, Taxi, massage you ask and she was available. I have never experienced somebody so dedicated to their job, and I was one of many she was handling. She is an incredible asset to this retreat. Thank you very much for making it a wonderful trip for me. All thanks to Helen the staff here
