Hsiu-Ying C wrote a review Dec 2023
Girls chill-out trip by the sea at Naman Retreat in Danang
Min is our host taking care of us during our 2-day stay at Naman Retreat. Food here is good, view is great and so are the buildings and facility. Package with spa everyday is superb to relax during the stay. Just a few suggestion, as weathe in Danang is humid, our stay can be even better if dehumidifier machine is available in each room. And welcome treats changing to afternoon tea set for 3 bedroom garden pool villa would be a plus. Post card delivery is not part of hotel service and thanks for Naman reception team’s help at our last day. Recommend to have post service in the future for international visitors keeping such great memory in written card. Thank you!
Dear valued Guest, Thank you for choosing Naman Retreat for your preferred stay in Da Nang. We are delighted to hear your feedback regarding your recent stay. Our Room is especially design to have tranquility and serinity for our guests. We always strive to deliver excellence for each aspect of our services and we are pleased to hear that Min has been attentive to you. Again, thank you for taking your time in writing this feedback. We hope to have the chance to welcome you back in the future. Should you have any inquiry, please do not hesitate to contact us. Kind Regards, Thao Pham Front Office Manager
